Kasancewar cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ta nuna irin wannan yanayin tsakanin kasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa a matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga ilimin da aka samu daga Italiya, dole ne kasar, asibitoci da kuma raka'a masu tsanani su kara shirye-shirye don samun saurin karuwa na marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawar lafiya da kuma kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu rahoton wani mummunan cutar pneumonia a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa an sake kiran sabon coronavirus a matsayin mai tasiri a matsayin cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 (Cov-2).
Saboda haka, an sanya sunan cutar ta hanyar kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 zuwa cutar Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Har zuwa yau, tabbataccen bayani shine cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 suna da wata cuta mai laushi, wato, kamuwa da cutar huhu tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin su sun warke.
Daga cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na wadanda suka kamu da cutar, COVID-19 ya zama mafi tsanani wanda ya haifar da bukatar shiga asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin dari na wadanda suka kamu da cutar suka kamu da mummunan rashin lafiya wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar da su daga asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna nazarin yanayin karuwar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU / European Economic Area (EU/EEA) da kuma a cikin United Kingdom (UK) da kuma kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya da adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Kasashen EU / EEA da UK sun sami COVID-19
Kasar Sin ta koma baya yayin da COVID-19 ke yaduwa a fannin duniya, kuma halin da COVID-19 ke fama da shi a sauran sassan duniya a halin yanzu yana bin kasar.
Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
A cikin EuroServAlance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon Turai da aka tabbatar da COVID-19 a matsayin sanarwa ta WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta sanar da cewa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, akwai mutane uku na farko da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da Burtaniya (UK) sun kamu da COVID-19, inda aka ba da rahoton 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 daga 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa kwanan wata da aka ambata, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da kuma karuwar yaduwar cutar
Cibiyar Tarayyar Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka da Kulawa (ECDC) ta ba da rahoton adadin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta duniya, wanda aka samu daga ma'aikatun lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da ƙasa da na yanki da kuma tushen gwamnati kamar WHO, wanda aka sabunta a kowace safiya da karfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan ne don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta abin da ya faru a Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na barkewar cutar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun lissafa kwanaki 14 na gajeren karuwar COVID-19, don haka muna la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19 na halitta a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jerin adadin shari'o'in da aka rubuta a kowace ƙasa har zuwa 8:00 na safe na 15 ga Maris 2020 idan aka kwatanta da waɗanda aka rubuta a Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Hanyoyin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya
Yanayin karuwar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya a cikin kwanaki 14 ya biyo bayan yanayin lardin Hubei (China) gaba ɗaya (Figure 1).
Ga EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya gabaɗaya, karuwar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ta karu da ƙarfi a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (ƙarin abu).
Wannan yafi haifar da saurin karuwa a cikin adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar karuwar abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 (abincin).
Hoton 2 ya kwatanta lambobin Italiya da yawan adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya don lokacin 31 Janairu-15 Maris 2020.
Ya kamata a lura cewa, a karfe 8:00 na safe na 15 ga Maris, sauran kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin da aka kwatanta da na Italiya a makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin sanannun shari'o'in COVID-19 suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin karuwar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna da matakan daban-daban, duk da bambancin martani ga lafiyar jama'a a cikin ƙasa, da kuma bambancin ƙayyadaddun masu kamuwa da cutar da kuma ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya a cikin ƙasashe waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kama-da-wane.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar ta COVID-19 a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin yada labarai sun bayyana cewa asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa a yankunan sun riga sun kai ga iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da shigar da COVID-19 a asibiti da / ko a cikin ICU a halin yanzu suna samuwa ne a cikin kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar a matakin EU / EEA, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su ta hanyar tsari don cika bayanan kulawa na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike a 2010-11 a kan yanayin gadaje 4.2 a kan yawan yara 100,000 a Jamus daga 29.2 a Portugal ya nuna babban bambanci tsakanin samun gadon kulawa mai tsanani da gadon kulawa na matsakaici a Turai.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙasa da ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (a cikin 201011 ana samun 12.5 a kowace 100,000 mutane da gadaje na kulawa ta tsakiya).
Idan aka duba yawan adadin COVID-19 da aka yi asibiti a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, yanayin samfurin haɗakar da iyawar kula da lafiya ya nuna cewa akwai > 90% na haɗarin lalacewar kwanciyar hankali a cikin gadon kulawa mai tsanani, wanda aka bayar a cikin sabuntawar shida na ECDC na COVID-19 Rapid Risk Assessment.
Tun da har yanzu ana samun cututtuka a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da wasu yankuna na Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa da gaggawa galibi suna ba da sabis na yanki ga jama'a, yana da kyau a sami bayanai game da marasa lafiya da wuraren kula da gaggawa ta hanyar tsarin suna na yanki don matakan Statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da kuma raka'a masu kulawa da gaggawa su shirya kansu don yanayin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 da ke gudana a cikin al'umma da kuma bukatar kula da lafiya da kuma kulawa mai tsanani, musamman ma, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da suka shafi Italiya, don karuwar yawan masu cutar COVID-19.
Kamar yadda ECDC ta kwanan nan ta nuna a cikin saurin kimanta haɗari, saurin, ingantaccen, da kuma daidaitaccen tsarin da ake buƙata don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da canji daga matsi zuwa ragewa, saboda idan ba a aiwatar da shi a kan lokaci ba, saurin saurin da ake tsammani na adadin shari'o'in zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci lokaci mai yawa don fahimta, karɓa da kuma samar da martani daidai.
Saurin tantance hadarin ya ba da jerin matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai gajeren lokaci na dama a lokacin da ƙasashe za su iya ƙara ƙoƙari don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsin lamba akan kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan bai yi nasara ba, akwai yiwuwar cewa tsarin kula da lafiya a sauran kasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin 'yan kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) da ta haifar da cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar da mutuwar mutane 3,000 a China da sauran duniya, kuma fiye da mutane 80,000 sun kamu da cutar, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga bil'adama.
